EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS IN PROGRESS UNTIL 181800Z NOV WITHIN:
   A. 40 MILES OF 57-43.5N 009-08.6W.
   B. 28 MILES OF 57-20.4N 008-18.4W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 181900Z NOV 15.
